How to choose a mattress and a sommier: women have other criteria than men.
Not ostentatious, but rather the quality of the surface area reserved for the 30dB, so the mattress and a sommier provide a real basis for a bed.
They must of course complement harmoniously to appeal to a specific user.
During the several things are decisive choice: weight, height, age, health status and sex of the owner.
The type of internal in which we will place the mattress and the sommier is also important.
A typical example?
For example in the house of campaign where you do not sleep continually latex mattresses are not appropriate because they "warm" slowly.
In addition, they have a higher weight polyurethane standards mattress.
It is necessary to return frequently.
If they do not have enough ventilation channels in the heart and, if they remain on a solid gameboard, they retain the moisture. Mould can also train.
The habit is also decisive in the choice.
Anyone who spends time clear abroad where it is often used mattresses very thick with a rammollissante layer, feel hardly naturally low and hard surface.
"This is all hokeyistes returning from NHL complain that they cannot sleep there."
"For their tired shoulders, feet and the coast, they need mattresses rammollisante with a layer of foam lazy."
"Such mattress is also recommended for people with diabetes have a disorder of the nervous system that take wrong" information "joints and the skin," Sylva Adamczikova who specializes in the upholstered furniture.
That is why there are a few years the mattress with foam lazy conquered the hokeyistes and other clients.
"Today everything, Tempur marcia, the Italian Magnifex but also the Czech Tropico for example appropriate mattress.
You do not need to be a guy NHL to assess a lazy foam.
This "miracle" simply works.
She make optimum its rigidity and its form in the heat absorbed or adapts to your body heat.
There is no pressure on you and you do not go back into the night as after a difficult match.
You simply sleep better.
The foam lazy works as a protection against the esquarres.
For the choice of mattress based on your size, add the length of the feet, or about 21/34 cm.
A man and a woman of a size of 180cm need a bed of 210/220 cm.
The minimum width for each for a bed to two places should be 90 cm by 180 cm.
For the beds in one place, the singles' for example, it is recommended to take at least 120/140 cm.
It is convenient to visit.
"It is a simple rule for the width of the bed: when you are lying on the back you should ask the hands of comfortable with elbows slightly bent. Helena Prokopova, President of the Association of Bourreliers - matelassiers and decorators dedicated to the issue of healthy sleep for several years and ergonomics furniture and teaches in the specialized schools.
For a bed to two places everyone needs its own sommier and mattresses, attention, however, during the achât to choose the height of the mattress.
Otherwise you will set up the sommier at different heights and this is not feasible on all executives of bed.
Foam mattresses should have a minimum height of 14 cm, mattresses springs at least 15 cm, that intend to form and ventilation layer at least three centimetres.
"The touchable or sit-stand on the mattress you must not feel springs," warned Héléna Prokopova.
Each mattress request a specific type of sommier.
The bed - sommier, when the mattress and siamoises are united as sisters, the sommier has nothing to do in the bedrooms.
The mattress aèrent very badly; we must not washing, which is commonly auhourd' Hui.
And since during the night it exudes 0.2 to 0.75 l sweat it is clear that after 5/7 years, the mattress begins to recall a great (and closed) Sieves.
For this the specialists refuse to advertise on a life span of 25 years for a mattress or a lifetime guarantee.
But his but.
And for this a board of experience of the sellers: for a mattress of 120/mitigating, for the lining of the mattress, give up hygiene or washing but add rather a mattress of protection that vouspouvez easily withdraw and washing.
And even if nowadays Lone-parenthood to produce coatings with closing up for the whole, that after the opening was two parties (for washing and the size of the washing machine is very important!) if not manipulation for large models (and for a single person) becomes when a fight between a small weight and a lorry cut in a ring.
You in your bed a rigid gameboard instead of a sommier?
Never!
The maximum for a bed to visitors for a single night.
However, équipez gameboard (if there is not) of aeration holes and use the mattress springs with a minimum height of 15cm with Add-to-Water springs (Germany Taschenfederken) and a layer of ventilation.
A polyurethane mattress should not be part of a bed of this type.
For the box slats with roles slat unique position, latex mattresses or Aeranautical sandwiches (perhaps the combination of latex-based and coconut), are the ideal but it is always better for you to have a mattress with slats, 28 and above, where the slats are doubled in the bottom part of the kidneys and that it is possible to regulate the rigidity.
For the mattress to several positions must not take mattress springs because it does not change of position.
Alongside the fine-tuning of the rigidity of slats can also install what is called a womb-to-tomb shoulder.
It is a special link slats that allows us to pressure or accept the lamelle for the shoulder of the Dungeness "fits."
For men who have "shoulders as wide as the backs," it is really an important thing.
This thing is already being considered by the manufacturers of mattresses for the "male" have begun to use a rammollissante area in the shoulders.
But they also believe women - they offer new more soft surface hip.
For the most difficult customer there is a over-wing box or platelets with what is called a multiforce suspension.
The pressure is released in more points and diinue tension.
But of course, attention, as soon as you use a bad pillow (large and inflated air) on good mattress and sommier, the "more" disappears.
The basic rule is a simple pillow; the pillow should support the head and its peaks must reach only the shoulders, so that the muscles of the shoulders can rest.
The recommended size is 50X60 cm preferred for example the Scandinavians.
When one is lying on the side, the pillow to level (with the cradle to shoulder the sommier or the rammollie area in the mattress) the height of the shoulders.
Modern mattresses have something in common with the first straw and herbs.
Manufacturers still use natural materials or mixtures.
The trend is also the organic mattress.
The raw materials based on pétrôle, which manufactures polyurethane, are replaced by natural oils such as soybean oil.
Almost all known manufacturers use precisely soybeans.
"The word Bio for mattresses means that the heart is made of natural products," Petr vasicek of the company Tropico Plus.
Natural materials are used for the coating mattresses; one of the first was the aloe vera.
But you can add macro-econometric capsules that develop perfumes of the forest or lavender.
There are differences between men and women.
While the extract birch plants for the mattress surface absorbs heat and any cooling of the body, "the man, coatings" hotter burn " women.
The extract of red pepper accelerates the blood-stream and is therefore more hot for sex.
The current favourites?
Mattresses manufactured from cold foam (she pores with a cellular structure law.24 more respirante than the standard polyurethane and has more elasticity.
The combination of different rigidities cold foams provides mattresses polyzones who know exactly where to find the head, the lower back and feet.
You will pay a quality mattress from 7,000 kroner and more.
Those who are characterized by their health parameters have less VAT and are taken as instruments for health.
In the Czech Republic, it is Gumotex who has reached the first place.
