The victory brought him popularity and be known over Libérec and its environs.
"The people I recognized in the streets, I often contentedly and, I must say, that it was very nice," he recalls.
It recommends participation in this competition to all those who are trying to do something.
This is not necessary to win but any opportunity to be visible is good.
He said that it uses up to now his contacts and knowledge that he would not have been able to obtain a different way.
"With those I met through the competition I started to maintain trade relations.
According to him, the famer linked to achieve has had an impact on employees.
And it has about 70.
"I observed among them especially loyalty and pride to be involved in something that has been generally recognized."
"This is not, and by far, the only result of my personal work, but the result of a good job of us all together.
"Only my name is pushed forward," said Lucas Pytloun with modesty.
