The special caliber ammunition for the rifle 25 mm developed and containing a highly explosive, works as small grenades.
The munitions can be programmed so that they explode on contact with the target, but also at any point in their ballistic trajectory.
We can therefore use against an enemy that hides behind a barrier, a wall or a gap.
