"I began to have my trip," she pesté, arguing that the PQ had been "dishonest" and had "failed to rigour."
She said that "this would be the least of things" that the PQ apologizes.
The formula is a common practice in the world.
It is usually a time-limited alliance that allows two or more companies to consolidate their respective expertise to respond to a tender for a complex project.
The project includes a high level of complexity given the scope of work.
The site is underway and properly until 2012.
However, the contract was awarded without competition should act; there have been negotiations.
Also, the formula is more an exception in Quebec, even for relatively simple projects.
